  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\nThere are several issues related to how pinned messages are shown on Android devices.\r\n\r\n\r\n#### ISSUE 1: white font on the pale gray background makes it hardly visible\r\n<img width=\"502\" alt=\"photo_2023-04-10 12 21 25 jpeg 2023-04-10 12-22-51\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/230883833-67679905-e0cb-4f6d-aa14-04860a977003.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n#### ISSUE 2: an audio message is hardly visible and cannot be played from pinned messages screen\r\n![IMAGE 2023-04-10 12:17:03](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/230882845-62b978c4-2fc0-47d8-8e28-f23e5d1a4254.jpg)\r\n\r\n\r\n#### ISSUE 3: white on white in the system messages (light mode only\r\n<img width=\"197\" alt=\"Monosnap 2023-04-10 12-38-02\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/230886305-062aea73-236f-440d-9c5e-8c33f36ebc47.png\">\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1) Open Status, pin several messages in a community\r\n2) Open pinned messages from an Android device and also pay attention to the system message \r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly 10/04/23\r\n- Operating System: Android\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
